TrekReady Hiking Boots is durable leather boots with reinforced stitching, toe protection, cushioned insoles, and breathable materials for comfort. BaseCamp Folding Table is lightweight aluminum table, 48 x 24 inches, foldable design. EcoFire Camping Stove is portable stainless steel stove, lightweight, fuel-efficient, and easy to use. CozyNights Sleeping Bag is lightweight, three-season sleeping bag designed for comfort and warmth during spring, summer, and fall. TrailWalker Hiking Shoes is synthetic leather and breathable mesh shoes with cushioned insoles, supportive midsoles, and excellent grip. MountainDream Sleeping Bag is three-season sleeping bag with premium synthetic insulation, suitable for temperatures down to 15Â°F.
